authors: Jessica Buchanan, Erik Landemalm, Anthony Flacco
data.meta_description: Buy Impossible Odds: The Kidnapping of Jessica Buchanan and Her Dramatic Rescue by SEAL Team Six by Jessica Buchanan, Erik Landemalm, Anthony Flacco in bulk from Porchlight Book Company (9781476725185)
data.text:
Jessica Buchanan worked in the humanitarian aid field in Somalia. She has recently relocated to the United States, where she and her husband, Erik Landemalm, lecture on their experiences while raising their son, August, born in October, 2012.
